{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/\u683c\u6597\u52a0\u9b54\u6cd5.gif?t=1735125701\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rune Coliseum is an action-packed gladiator battle simulator that combines elements from deck-building, fighting, and roguelike games. Pick a character, prepare for a duel, and enter the deadly tournament where only one can emerge as the victor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/\u51fa\u724c.gif?t=1735125701\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master the unique combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A unique turn-based combat system where you can perform multiple actions in a single turn; it combines strategic depth with smooth animations. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose Your Fighter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/\u5934\u50cf.png?t=1735125701\" />Pick one gladiator from many to start the battle, each with unique skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/\u5fc5\u6740\u6280.gif?t=1735125701\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/\u6b66\u5668.png?t=1735125701\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experiment with Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plunder a wide variety of weapons and equipment from other players on the battlefield, or purchase them at shops. Each item has its own unique skills, allowing you to customize your playstyle and tactics to suit your preferences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><im